tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE land_use_changes (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    date DATE,
    area DECIMAL,
    land_use_type VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE LandUse { 
   land_use_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
   parcel_id INT, 
   land_use_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL, 
   land_use_start_date DATE, 
   land_use_end_date DATE 
}
